---

<section class="knit-section">
    <div class="knit-container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <h2 class="section-title">Why Cookingdom is the Ultimate Cozy Escape</h2>
            <p class="section-subtitle">Discover the sensory details and relaxing mechanics that make Cookingdom a top-rated culinary simulation</p>
        </div>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-icon bg-blue-100 text-knitBlue">
                        <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Mindful, No-Timer Gameplay</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">Unlike stressful time-management games, <strong>Cookingdom</strong> lets you cook at your own pace. Experience a <strong>relaxing cooking simulation</strong> where every chop, stir, and flip is a mindful action designed to decompress your mind, not test your reflexes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-icon bg-green-100 text-knitGreen">
                        <i class="fas fa-headphones-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Deeply Satisfying ASMR Audio</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">Immerse yourself in "sounds you can feel." From the crisp crunch of fresh veggies to the gentle sizzle of a steak, the high-quality <strong>ASMR sound design</strong> paired with soft <strong>lo-fi beats</strong> creates a warm, auditory blanket for your ears.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-icon bg-purple-100 text-knitPurple">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe-asia"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Authentic World Cuisines</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">Your recipe book is a passport to flavor. Unlock and master hundreds of <strong>global recipes</strong>—from fluffy Japanese pancakes and Tonkotsu ramen to spicy Texas BBQ and traditional Mooncakes. Explore rich cultures through their <strong>comfort foods</strong>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="feature-card">
                <div class="card-content">
                    <div class="card-icon bg-pink-100 text-knitPink">
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="card-title">Build Your Dream Kitchen</h3>
                    <p class="card-text">Turn your culinary space into a sanctuary. Customize your environment with fairy lights, rustic shelves, and cute <strong>cat-themed kitchen tools</strong>. Every level you pass rewards you with decor to create the perfect <strong>cozy aesthetic</strong>.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* 功能区样式 */
    .knit-section {
        padding: 80px 0;
        background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff, #fef7f0);
    }

    .knit-container {
        max-width: 1200px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
    }

    /* 标题区域样式 */
    .section-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }

    .section-title {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cooking-orange), var(--cooking-red));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
        line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .section-subtitle {
        font-size: 1.25rem;
        color: var(--knit-gray);
        max-width: 768px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .section-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
        }
        
        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
        }
    }

    /* 功能网格布局 */
    .features-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    @media (min-width: 1024px) {
        .features-grid {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        }
    }

    /* 卡片样式 */
    .feature-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: var(--radius-large);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);
        transition: var(--transition);
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.1);
    }

    .feature-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .card-content {
        padding: 2rem;
        height: 100%;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }

    .card-icon {
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        transition: var(--transition);
    }

    .feature-card:hover .card-icon {
        transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    .card-title {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        text-align: center;
        color: var(--knit-dark);
    }

    .card-text {
        color: var(--knit-gray);
        line-height: 1.6;
        text-align: center;
        flex: 1;
    }

    .card-text strong {
        color: var(--cooking-orange);
        font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* 图标背景色 */
    .bg-blue-100 { background-color: rgba(52, 152, 219, 0.1); }
    .bg-green-100 { background-color: rgba(46, 204, 113, 0.1); }
    .bg-purple-100 { background-color: rgba(155, 89, 182, 0.1); }
    .bg-pink-100 { background-color: rgba(232, 67, 147, 0.1); }

    /* 图标颜色 */
    .text-knitBlue { color: var(--knit-blue); }
    .text-knitGreen { color: var(--knit-green); }
    .text-knitPurple { color: var(--knit-purple); }
    .text-knitPink { color: var(--knit-pink); }

    /* Font Awesome 图标 */
    .fa-leaf:before { content: "\f06c"; }
    .fa-headphones-alt:before { content: "\f58f"; }
    .fa-globe-asia:before { content: "\f57e"; }
    .fa-home:before { content: "\f015"; }
    
    .fas {
        font-family: "Font Awesome 6 Free";
        font-weight: 900;
    }
</style>